oauth_django17
==============

oauth example with django-oauth-toolkit based on django 1.7


Primitives
==========
-	^login/$  
        Login goes directly to django.contrib.auth.views.login. --> when login is successful then redirects to app_profile (registration/profile)
-	^logout/$
-	^password_change/$
-	^password_change/done/$
-	^password_reset/$
-	^password_reset/done/$
-	^reset/(?P<uidb36>[0-9A-Za-z]+)-(?P<token>.+/$
-	^reset/done/$
-	^signup/$
-	^signup/done/$
-	^signup/(?P<uidb36>[0-9A-Za-z]+)-(?P<token>.+)/$
-	^signup/complete/$
-	^profile/$

